Hello everyone 
Tomorrow starts my 30day countdown to my 30th ! My birthday theme this year is LOVE❤️ We all know LOVE is KIND . Please join me in 30 Acts of Kindness for the next 30 days . Your participation means the most to me ! Post and tag me showcasing your acts of kindness … May 4th -June 4th ❤️❤️
She’s back 🫶🏾

May 5th Day 2: Pay it forward! The original plan was to bless my valet at my house but God had other plans ! Im so full of joy to do this challenge! Thank you so much to Ms.Donna at target in the galleria area, for helping me see the bigger picture ❤️🤍 The best feeling in the world is to be a blessing 🫶🏾🤍 please tag and post your acts of kindness #30actsofkindness #30before30

May 6th Day 3: SPA DAY!!! I love the spa so much it helps me reset, realign, and recharge . The older I get the more I learn if you are kind to yourself, you are kind to others. Treat yourself to a spa day or gift a spa day to someone else ❤️🤍🫶🏾 #30actsofkindness
May 9th Day 6: Help the homeless! Even tho I had other plans God put me exactly where I needed to be 🤍🫶🏾 #30actsofkindness please joins and participate .
